title: Widespread Panic - Red Rocks, Morrison, CO
description:
6.27.2013 | Red Rocks | Morrison, CO | 7:50 MDT
Set 1:	A of D > Rock, Better Off > Weak Brain/Narrow Mind, Dyin' Man, Bear's Gone Fishin', Walkin' (For Your Love), Pickin' Up The Pieces, You'll Be Fine, Knocking 'Round The Zoo [61 mins]
Set 2:	Weight of the World, Papa Johnny Road > Party At Your Mama's House > Ribs & Whiskey, Papa's Home > Blue Indian > Drums > Papa Legba > Papa's Home > Sewing Machine, Red Hot Mama [86 mins]
Encore:	Don't Be Denied, Hope In A Hopeless World
Notes:	[Soundcheck on 06/26/13: 'You'll Be Fine', 'Cream Puff War'; Last 'You'll Be Fine' - 02/10/11, 125 shows; 'Pusherman' and 'Down On The Farm' teases during 'Party At Your Mama's House'; 'Rock On' tease after 'Ribs And Whiskey'; 'Sewing Machine' tease before 'Blue Indian'; 'Everybody Wants You' jam after 'Drums'; 'Protein Drink' tease before 'Papa Legba'; Mamas & Papas-themed 2nd set & encore
